   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COMPLETION OF BLOOD BANK FOR TRANSFUSION SERVICES</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The ECG hospital is located in kpandai, a rural community with a population of about 108,816. The hospital carry out emergency operations that need the availability of blood and blood products. Also, antepartum hemorrhage, post partum hemorrhage and anemia cases need urgent transfusion.  However we do not have a standard blood bank and our services are hampered by such a deficiency. We are therefore rolling out this project in order to procure a blood bank and refurbish a room for this services</narrative>
  </description>
